McDonaldPeakMontana.jpg|18. [[McDonald Peak]] is the highest summit of the [[Mission Mountains]] of Montana.
Pikes Peak CO.jpg|19. [[Pikes Peak]] in Colorado was the inspiration for ''[[America the Beautiful]]''.
MtBlancaEast.jpg|25. [[Blanca Peak]] is the highest summit of the [[Sangre de Cristo Mountains]] of Colorado.
Mount Cleveland.jpg|28. [[Mount Cleveland (Montana)|Mount Cleveland]] is the highest summit of the [[Lewis Range]] of Montana.
