The [[Solomon Islands]] requires its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display '''[[vehicle registration plate]]s'''.<ref>http://www.plateshack.com/y2k/Solomon_Islands/solomony2k.htm</ref> Current plates are [[Vehicle registration plates of Australia|Australian standard]] 372 mm × 134 mm.<ref>http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/PA_SOLO.html</ref> {|class="wikitable" |- !Image !First issued !Design !Slogan !Serial format !Serials issued !Notes |- |[[File:Solomon Islands license plate graphic.png|150px]] | | | | | | |- |}
==References== <references />
